import DocsLayout from "../../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro";
---

<DocsLayout title="Quick start" description="Run tokenuse, navigate the dashboard, and learn the core keyboard shortcuts.">
  <p class="docs-eyebrow">QUICK START</p>
  <h1>Run the local dashboard</h1>
  <p class="docs-lede">
    Clone the repository, run the Rust TUI, and use a terminal at least 120x40. Smaller terminals show a resize notice
    instead of the full dashboard.
  </p>

  <pre><code>git clone https://github.com/russmckendrick/tokenuse
cd tokenuse
cargo run</code></pre>

  <h2>What happens on startup</h2>
  <p>
    tokenuse scans local session files from supported AI coding tools, normalizes project names, and renders spend by day,
    project, tool, model, shell command, and MCP server. If no local sessions are found, or ingestion fails before any calls
    are loaded, the app falls back to bundled sample data and shows that status in the title bar.
  </p>

  <h2>Dashboard panels</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Summary totals for cost, calls, sessions, cache hit rate, input, output, cache reads, and cache writes.</li>
    <li>Daily cost and call activity.</li>
    <li>Spend by project, project/tool pair, top sessions, and model.</li>
    <li>Core tool calls, shell command heads, and MCP server usage.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="keyboard">Keyboard</h2>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr><th>Key</th><th>Action</th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><kbd>q</kbd> or <kbd>Esc</kbd></td><td>Quit</td></tr>
      <tr><td><kbd>1</kbd> to <kbd>5</kbd></td><td>Switch between today, 7 days, 30 days, this month, and all time</td></tr>
      <tr><td><kbd>t</kbd></td><td>Cycle tool filter</td></tr>
      <tr><td><kbd>p</kbd></td><td>Open project picker</td></tr>
      <tr><td><kbd>c</kbd></td><td>Open configuration</td></tr>
      <tr><td><kbd>s</kbd></td><td>Open session picker and drill into one session</td></tr>
      <tr><td><kbd>u</kbd></td><td>Open usage page</td></tr>
      <tr><td><kbd>e</kbd></td><td>Export the current view as JSON, CSV, SVG, or PNG</td></tr>
      <tr><td><kbd>r</kbd></td><td>Reload ingestion in place</td></tr>
      <tr><td><kbd>h</kbd> or <kbd>?</kbd></td><td>Open the keybinding reference</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2>Configuration</h2>
  <p>
    Runtime settings live in the platform config directory under <code>tokenuse</code>. USD remains the default display currency.
    Costs are calculated and stored internally as USD, then converted for display using the configured currency.
  </p>

  <pre><code>cargo run --features refresh-currency,refresh-prices</code></pre>

  <h2>CLI helpers</h2>
  <pre><code>cargo run -- --list-projects
cargo run --features refresh-prices -- --refresh-prices
cargo run --features refresh-currency -- --generate-currency-json</code></pre>
</DocsLayout>
